<Layout
  title="Why Wrapper Apps Are Better Than Native Apps"
  description="Find out why MobiLoud is the best way to build iOS and Android wrapper apps from your website or web app, and how a web wrapper lets you build full featured mobile apps!"
>
  <Nav />

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 px-4">
